WEBVTT

00:01:58.237 --> 00:02:01.635
siz inson bo'lish qanaqaligini anglatuvchi
qismini o'tkazib yuborgansiz.

00:02:01.635 --> 00:02:06.125
Ko'plab mutafakkirlar melanxoliya 
donishmandlik uchun muhim degan.

00:02:06.125 --> 00:02:08.798
1577-yilda tug'ilgan Robert Byorton

00:02:08.798 --> 00:02:12.896
butun umrini qayg'uning sababi va 
tajribasini o'rganish bilan o'tkazgan.

00:02:12.896 --> 00:02:16.011
O'zining
"Melanxoliya anatomiyasi"

00:02:16.011 --> 00:02:20.909
asarida: "Donishmandlikni nima oshirsa, 
u qayg'uni ham oshiradi" degan.

00:02:20.909 --> 00:02:23.758
XIX asr romantik shoirlari ishonishganki,

00:02:23.758 --> 00:02:29.016
melanxoliya bizga boshqa murakkab hislarni
yaxshiroq tushunishga yordam beradi.

00:02:29.016 --> 00:02:30.603
Masalan, go'zallik va rohat.